        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK111">
<l>takuti yeṉavoṉṟu naṉṟē pakutiyāṟ</l>
<l>pāṟpaṭṭa ṭoḻukap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That equity which consists in acting with equal regard to each of (the three) divisions of men [enemies, strangers and friends] is a pre-eminent virtue.</l>
            </lg>
